==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interconnect
<hw>In`ter*con*nect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To join
together; to connect with one another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interconnect</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Interconnect
<hw>In`ter*con*nect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To become
connected with one another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>interconnected</ent>⟦br⟧
